---
  import Layout from "../layouts/layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About" description="MEP Consulting company">
  <main class="pt-20 pb-20 px-6 flex flex-col gap-10">
    <section class="prose">
      <h1>About</h1>

      <p>AJ Design group was founded in 2003???? with a mission to provide top-quality mechanical, electrical and
        plumbing engineering designs for all construction projects. We are based in Los Angeles but our work spans
        <strong> Los Angeles County</strong>, <strong>San Diego County</strong>,<strong>Orange County</strong>, and
        <strong>Ventura County</strong>.
      </p>

      <p>Our engineers specialize in</p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2">
        <ul>
          <li>MEP</li>
          <li>Mechanical</li>
          <li>Electrical</li>
          <li>Plumbing</li>
          <li>Title 24</li>
        </ul>

        <ul>
          <li>Fire Sprinklers</li>
          <li>Gas</li>
          <li>Sewer</li>
          <li>Solar</li>
          <li>Lighting</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="flex flex-col gap-4">
      <div class="prose">
        <h1>Our Leaders</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-10 md:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
          <a href="/team/joey-jiron"><img src="/img/joeyjiron.png" alt="Joey Jiron" /></a>
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="card-title">Joey Jiron</div>
            <p>Principal | Mechanical Engineer</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
          <a href="/team/joey-jiron"><img src="/img/joeyjiron.png" alt="Joey Jiron" /></a>
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="card-title">Joey A</div>
            <p>Partner | Electrical Engineer</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>


    <section class="prose">
      <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

      <p>Here are some answers to the most comment questions we receive. Please feel free to contact us if you do not
        see your question answered below.</p>

      <div tabindex="0" class="collapse collapse-arrow border border-base-300 bg-base-100 rounded-box">
        <input type="checkbox" />

        <div class="collapse-title text-xl font-medium">
          Where are we located?
        </div>
        <div class="collapse-content">
          <p>We are proud to be licensed in 15 states and counting. Our main offices are located in San Diego and Orange
            County.</p>
        </div>
      </div>


      <div tabindex="0" class="collapse collapse-arrow border border-base-300 bg-base-100 rounded-box">
        <input type="checkbox" />
        <div class="collapse-title text-xl font-medium">
          Do you do custom work?
        </div>
        <div class="collapse-content">
          <p>We do it all! Whether you’ve got a custom commercial, industrial, or residential, project that requires
            engineering consulting, we’ve got you covered.</p>
        </div>
      </div>


      <div tabindex="0" class="collapse collapse-arrow border border-base-300 bg-base-100 rounded-box">
        <input type="checkbox" />
        <div class="collapse-title text-xl font-medium">
          What services do you offer?
        </div>
        <div class="collapse-content">
          <p>Our engineers specialize in</p>

          <ul>
            <li>MEP</li>
            <li>Mechanical</li>
            <li>Electrical</li>
            <li>Plumbing</li>
            <li>Title 24</li>
            <li>Fire Sprinklers</li>
            <li>Gas</li>
            <li>Sewer</li>
            <li>Solar</li>
            <li>Lighting</li>
            <li>Heat Load Calculations</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div tabindex="0" class="collapse collapse-arrow border border-base-300 bg-base-100 rounded-box">
        <input type="checkbox" />
        <div class="collapse-title text-xl font-medium">
          What does MEP stand for?
        </div>
        <div class="collapse-content">
          <p>MEP stands for mechanical, electrical, and plumbing. AJ Design Group develops engineering plans for your
            contractor.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div tabindex="0" class="collapse collapse-arrow border border-base-300 bg-base-100 rounded-box">
        <input type="checkbox" />
        <div class="collapse-title text-xl font-medium">
          Who are your typical clients?
        </div>
        <div class="collapse-content">
          <p>We typically work with architects, designers, general contractors, and design-build contracts. We also deal
            directly with property/business owners.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>